== 機隊 ==
截至2021年8月，馬來西亞航空平均機齡9年 機隊如下<ref name=chaviationch>[http://www.ch-aviation.ch/portal/airline.php?cha=MH Malaysia Airlines Fleet] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ch-aviation.ch/portal/airline.php?cha=MH |date=20131114034131 }} ''ch-aviation.ch''</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Fleet (Malaysia Airlines - Fleet) |publisher=Malaysia Airlines |url=http://www.malaysiaairlines.com/au/en/mh-experience/our-fleet/boeing-737-800.html |access-date=2013-06-29 |archive-date=2018-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818214747/https://www.malaysiaairlines.com/au/en/mh-experience/our-fleet/boeing-737-800.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=planespotters>{{cite web|author=6 March 2014|url=http://www.planespotters.net/Airline/Malaysia-Airlines|title=Malaysia Airlines Fleet in Planespotters.net|publisher=planespotters.net|date=|accessdate=2014-03-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314132451/http://www.planespotters.net/Airline/Malaysia-Airlines|archivedate=2014年3月14日}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.planespotters.net/airline/Malaysia-Airlines |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-03-21 |archive-date=2019-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190425211647/https://www.planespotters.net/airline/Malaysia-Airlines |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
